sequenceDiagram
  actor Student
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant API as API Server
  participant MQ as Message Queue
  participant Worker as Worker Process
  participant Sandbox as Docker Sandbox
  participant DB as MongoDB

  Student->>UI: Submit code
  UI->>API: POST submission
  API->>DB: Save submission as QUEUED
  API->>MQ: Publish job
  API-->>UI: Return submission id
  Worker->>MQ: Pull job
  Worker->>Sandbox: Run code with limits
  Sandbox-->>Worker: Output and verdict
  Worker->>DB: Save final result
  UI->>API: Poll status
  API->>DB: Read result
  API-->>UI: Return result
  UI-->>Student: Show score
